				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Have a character interact with one of these (you can buy it from Tolna):\r\n\r\nS_LOW_SightOfTheSeelie\r\nS_LOW_CurriculumStrategy\r\nS_LOW_KarsusNotes\r\n\r\n, get the curse and then have another character read the same book.\r\n\r\nCTY_Main_A 8; 26; -93"
				},
